    <!--****TAG EXPLAINATATION****
        
    - Who             Refers to the owner of this dialogue
                      Check the PERSON_ID from the gamecontrol script in enum Ally
                      
    - Speaker         The person that is currently speaking; Either the NPC or the PLAYER
    
    - TYPE            D for normal dialogues  
                      E for ending dialogues
                      S for special dialogues
                      
    - Line            Used for identifying the line number of the conversation
    
    - Text            The sentence itself
    **************************-->
    <!--*****IMPORTANT****
    - Formatting      It is A MUST to follow the exact format
    
    - PERSON_ID       Please refer from the gamecontrol script in enum Ally
    
    - ID              Starts from 0
    
    - LINE_NO         Starts from 0
    
    - Speaker         ALWAYS IN CAPS
    
    - Text            Needs proof reading
                      Punctuations; Don't forget the full stops/periods, question marks, etc, wherever it's needed
                  
    - DEAD_FRIEND_ID  The name is self explainatory
                      Please refer from the gamecontrol script in enum Ally
                      
    IF YOU NEED MORE INFORMATION PLEASE ASK ME RIGHT AWAY
    ******************-->
